---
APPENDIX C: BITWISE OPERATORS

The code in this directory is related to
the material in Appenix C in

   C By Dissection, 4th edition,
   Al Kelley and Ira Pohl,
   Addison-Wesley, San Francisco, 2001

---
Files ending in .c contain either C or C++ programs
that are ready to be compiled and executed.

Each subdirectory may contain .h and .c files that
comprise a single C or C++ program, or it may
contain programs such as

   pgm1.c   pgm2.c   ...

that are a variation on a theme.
